<HL>
   Who's News:
   Abiomed's Singh Takes
   Indefinite Leave of Absence
</HL>
<DATE>
05/21/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   ABD WNEWS
</CO>
<LP>
   DANVERS, Mass. -- Abiomed Inc. said Param I. Singh has
decided to go on indefinite leave of absence and resign from
his position as executive vice president effective Aug. 1.
   Dr. Singh, who was also general manager of the company's
Abiodent dental division, said in a news release that the
decision "was based entirely on health reasons." He will
continue to serve as an Abiomed director.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Abiomed develops medical and dental devices and cardiac
support systems.
</TEXT>
